ponsibility.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe's%20discovered%20a%20love%20of%20creating%20baked%20goods%2C%20and%20our%20family%20gets%20to%20enjoy%20them.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe's%20also%20become%20more%20self-sufficient%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20win%20for%20everyone.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20my%2011-year-old%20announced%20his%20school's%20upcoming%20bake%20sale%2C%20I%20braced%20for%20a%20request%20I%20wasn't%20prepared%20for%20%E2%80%94%20baking.%20%26quot%3BYou%20know%20I%20don't%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdepression-cake-recipe-no-eggs-dairy-review-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eenjoy%20baking%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20reminded%20him%2C%20expecting%20disappointment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20instead%20of%20pushing%20back%2C%20he%20had%20a%20plan%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20need%20you%20to%20bake%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20He%20knew%20his%20older%20brother%2C%2014%2C%20would%20handle%20it.%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20need%20you%20to%20help%20with%20managing%20the%20cash%20at%20the%20counter.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20that%20moment%2C%20I%20realized%20something%20powerful%20%E2%80%94%20by%20stepping%20back%2C%20I%20had%20unintentionally%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwe-give-our-kids-independence-in-stages-but-they-also-have-responsabilities-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epushed%20my%20son%20toward%20self-sufficiency%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cab0a1ed-af1f-40c5-9621-b7758f4f422f%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ELetting%20my%20eldest%20take%20the%20lead%20has%20been%20a%20lesson%20for%20both%20of%20us%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20my%20life%2C%20I%20saw%20cooking%20as%20a%20basic%20survival%20skill%2C%20not%20a%20passion%2C%20unlike%20my%20grandpa%2C%20mom%2C%20and%20sister%20who%20all%20loved%20to%20spend%20time%20in%20the%20kitchen%20cooking.%20I%20can%20manage%20boiling%2C%20saut%C3%A9ing%2C%20roasting%2C%20and%20deep-frying%2C%20I%20never%20explored%20baking%3B%20it%20was%20an%20intimidating%20mystery.%20But%20my%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbenefits-of-only-child-more-time-financial-relief-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etwo%20children%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20drawn%20to%20the%20cakes%20and%20pizzas%20they%20loved%2C%20took%20matters%20into%20their%20own%20hands.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20we%20moved%20from%20India%20to%20Canada%20four%20years%20ago%2C%20my%20eldest%20started%20small%20%E2%80%94%20ready-to-bake%20cookie%20mixes%20from%20the%20grocery%20store.%20But%20soon%2C%20he%20was%20watching%20YouTube%20tutorials%2C%20baking%20from%20scratch%2C%20tweaking%20recipes%2C%20and%20even%20experimenting%20with%20his%20own%20versions.%20His%20most%20recent%20creation%20was%20a%20brownie%20loaded%20with%20chocolate%20chips%2C%20chewy%20candies%2C%20M%26amp%3BMs%2C%20and%20Oreos%20%E2%80%94%20making%20it%20almost%20intolerably%20sweet.%20But%20hey%2C%20they're%20kids%3B%20don't%20they%20all%20love%20to%20overdo%20it%20on%20sugar%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe's%20made%20mistakes%20%E2%80%94%20rock-hard%20cookies%2C%20overly%20salty%20cakes%20%E2%80%94%20but%20each%20failure%20became%20a%20learning%20moment.%20Each%20time%20something%20went%20wrong%2C%20he%20retraced%20his%20steps%20to%20identify%20what%20needed%20to%20change.%20He%20hasn't%20mastered%20icing%20yet%20and%20still%20uses%20store-bought%20options%2C%20but%20he's%20determined%20to%20figure%20it%20out.%20His%20short-term%20goal%3F%20Learn%20the%20right%20temperature%20to%20ice%20a%20cake%20and%20eventually%20create%20his%20own%20frosting%20flavors%2C%20inspired%20by%20the%20%26quot%3BIs%20It%20Cake%3F%26quot%3B%20show.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223ead7aca-dd8f-42f3-