t%3B%20said%20CFRA%20Research's%20Nelson.%20However%2C%20Nelson%20said%20Tesla's%20competitors%20may%20be%20more%20%26quot%3Bexposed%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20like%20General%20Motors%2C%20which%20has%20significant%20production%20and%20sourcing%20in%20Mexico%20and%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20doesn't%20mean%20Tesla%20would%20be%20unaffected%20though.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvesting.com's%20Monteiro%20told%20BI%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20no%20question%26quot%3B%20that%20%26quot%3BTesla's%20margins%20will%20be%20pressured%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20coming%20quarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariffs-mexico-canada-impact-tesla-rivian-ford-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla's%20final%20assembly%20takes%20place%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20National%20Highway%20Traffic%20Safety%20Administration%20filing%20indicated%20between%2020%25%20and%2025%25%20of%20the%20company's%20components%20from%20its%202025%20model-year%20vehicles%20were%20sourced%20from%20Mexico.%20Tesla's%202023%20Impact%20Report%20also%20shows%20that%20the%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tesla.com%2Fns_videos%2F2023-tesla-impact-report.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esources%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20number%20of%20materials%20abroad%20for%20its%20battery%20and%20auto%20parts%20production%2C%20including%20lithium%2C%20nickel%2C%20steel%2C%20and%20iron.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMonteiro%20said%20further%20domesticating%20the%20supply%20chain%20would%20be%20expensive%20and%20the%20company's%20strategy%20of%20periodically%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-promotion-incentives-free-supercharging-full-self-driving-fsd-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereducing%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20sell%20more%20cars%20would%20%26quot%3Bbecome%20even%20worse%20from%20a%20financial%20standpoint.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20talk%20numbers%2C%20a%2025%25%20tariff%20would%20amount%20to%20a%20cost%20increase%20of%20around%20%241.5%20billion%20in%20the%20first%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20Monteiro%20estimated%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20cost%20would%20likely%20improve%20as%20company%20supply%20chains%20adapt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228514817d-60c8-4d4b-9111-7d6d3248107d%5C%22%3EMusk%20has%20largely%20shrugged%20off%20the%20potential%20impacts%20on%20Tesla's%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20also%20talked%20about%20rolling%20back%20Biden's%20EV%20incentives%2C%20including%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-electric-vehicle-tax-credit-ira-biden-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInflation%20Reduction%20Act%20passed%20in%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20offers%20buyers%20a%20federal%20tax%20break%20of%20up%20to%20%247%2C500%20for%20new%20EVs%20and%20a%20%244%2C000%20credit%20for%20used%20EVs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20lowering%20the%20overall%20price%20of%20buying%20a%20Tesla%20has%20benefited%20the%20company%2C%20Musk%20has%20voiced%20support%20for%20eliminating%20EV%20tax%20credits%20on%20several%20occasions%20%E2%80%94%20something%20not%20all%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-shareholders-elon-musk-doge-trump-politics-focus-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla%20shareholders%3C%2Fa%3E%20agree%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it%20would%20be%20devastating%20for%20our%20competitors%20and%20for%20Tesla%20slightly%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said%20in%20a%20July%20earnings%20call%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-tesla-elon-musk-supports-trump-ending-ev-tax-credits-2024-11%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIts%2520market%2520lead%2520is%2520well%2Chalf%2520were%2520made%2520by%2520Tesla.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etax%20credits%20ending%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BBut%20long-term%20probably%20actually%20helps%20Tesla%2C%20would%20be%20my%20guess.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20he's%20right%2C%20the%20move%20could%20help%20Tesla%20maintain%20its%20dominance%20in%20the%20US%20EV%20market%2C%20especially%20after%20its%20estimated%20market%20share%20fell%20below%2050%25%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENelson%20said%20Musk's%20position%20is%20likely%20that%20Tesla%20has%20a%20strong%20brand%20value%20and%20its%20buyers%20tend%20to%20be%20higher%20income.%20That%20means%20the%20tax%20credits%20may%20not%20be%20%26quot%3Bas%20much%20a%20factor%20in%20their%20purchase%20decision%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20also%20moved%20to%20repeal%20the%20Biden-era%20EV%20mandates%2C%20which%20aimed%20to%20boost%20EV%20adoption%20through%20investments%20in%20infrastructure%20like%20charging%20stations%20and%20stricter%20emission%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20first%20day%20back%20in%20office%2C%20Trump%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fpresidential-actions%2F2025%2F01%2Funleashing-american-energy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esigned%3C%2Fa%3E%20an%20executive%20order%20%26quot%3Bto%20eliminate%20the%20'electric%20vehicle%20(EV)%20mandate'%20and%20promote%20true%20consumer%20choice.%26quot%3B%20The%20order%20calls%20for%20the%20removal%20of%20state%20emissions%20waivers%20that%20work%20to%20limit%20sales%20of%20auto%20vehicles%20and%20other%20government%20policies%20that%20%26quot%3Bfavor%20EVs%20over%20other%20technologies%2C%26quot%3B%20mandating%20their%20purchase%20by%20making%20%26quot%3Bother%20types%20of%20vehicles%20unaffordable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20on%20social%20media%20over%20the%20summer%20about%20Trump's%20proposed%20EV%20policies%2C%20Musk%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1814664480044748999%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20time%20that%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20will%20be%20fine%26quot%3B%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1814165239602012523%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%26quot%3Ba%20surprising%20number%20of%20people%20think%20that%20Tesla%20survives%20on%20subsidies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20true%20of%20our%20competitors%2C%20but%20not%20of%20Tesla%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20pulling%20back%20Biden's%20EV%20mandates%20on%20emissions%20targets%20threatens%20Tesla's%20revenue%20stream%20from%20selling%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tesla-ev-credits-elon-musk-regulation-2025-1%3Futm_source%3Dchatgpt.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eregulatory%20credits%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20automakers%20that%20fail%20to%20meet%20federal%20and%20state%20EV%20sales%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20fourth%20quarter%2C%20Tesla%20reported%20%24692%20million%20in%20revenue%20from%20these%20credits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20really%20no%20cost%20associated%20with%20that%20revenue%2C%20so%20it's%20basically%20got%20100%25%20margin%20and%20it%20flows%20right%20through%20the%20bottom%20line%2C%26quot%3B%20Nelson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStephanie%20Valdez%20Streaty%2C%20a%20director%20of%20industry%20insights%20at%20Cox%20Automotive%2C%20previously%20told%20BI%20that%2C%20%26quot%3BTesla%20has%20relied%20on%20the%20credits%20to%20help%20really%20boost%20profitability.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20federal%20guidelines%20are%20less%20stringent%2C%20then%20other%20manufacturers%20have%20more%20time%2C%20and%20they're%20not%20going%20to%20need%20those%20credits%20as%20much%2C%20so%20I%20think%20it'll%20definitely%20impact%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-tesla-impact-trump-tariffs-ev-mandate-tax-credits-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739705581000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F679d32467