ncis-sits-out-sunday-mass%2Farticleshow%2F118302454.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fin-hospital-a-resting-pope-francis-sits-out-sunday-mass%2Famp_articleshow%2F118302454.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fin-hospital-a-resting-pope-francis-sits-out-sunday-mass%2Famp_articleshow%2F118302454.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Minister%20On%20How%20Nuclear%20Technology%20Is%20Helping%20Maintain%20Hygiene%20At%20Kumbh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20%26quot%3Bno%20sign%20of%20any%20disease%20outbreak%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20even%20though%20millions%20are%20taking%20a%20bath%20at%20Prayagraj%2C%20asserted%20the%20country's%20science%20minister%2C%20attributing%20it%20to%20the%20wonders%20of%20nuclear%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20estimated%20that%20by%20now%20more%20than%20500%20million%20have%20taken%20a%20bath%20at%20the%20confluence%20of%20Ganga%2C%20Yamuna%20and%20the%20lost%20river%20Saraswati.%20To%20put%20this%20massive%20number%20in%20perspective%20--%20it%20is%20more%20than%20the%20combined%20populations%20of%20USA%20and%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMore%20than%2050%20crore%20devotees%20have%20already%20visited%20and%20yet%20no%20sign%20of%20hygiene%20disruption%20or%20epidemic%20risk%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Science%20minister%20Dr%20Jitendra%20Singh%20--%20also%20the%20Minister%20of%20State%20in%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20Office%20-%20who%20visited%20the%20Sangam%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20trained%20diabetologist%20and%20a%20practicing%20physician%2C%20Dr%20Singh%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3BHerculean%20task%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20unique%20feat%20has%20been%20made%20possible%20thanks%20to%20the%20deployment%20of%20unique%20Indian%20sewage%20treatment%20plants%20that%20have%20been%20pioneered%20by%20the%20Bhabha%20Atomic%20Research%20Center%20(BARC)%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20Center%20for%20Atomic%20Research%20(IGCAR)%2C%20Kalpakkam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20institutions%20are%20affiliated%20to%20the%20Department%20of%20Atomic%20Energy.%3Cbr%3E%5CnA%20sewage%20treatment%20system%20named%20Hybrid%20granular%20Sequencing%20Batch%20Reactors%20or%20hgSBR%20technology%20has%20been%20deployed%20at%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20plants%20use%20microbes%20to%20treat%20the%20dirty%20water%20and%20are%20often%20called%20Fecal%20Sludge%20Treatment%20Plants.%20The%20technology%20has%20been%20researched%20and%20developed%20by%20Dr%20Venkat%20Nancharaiah%2C%20who%20works%20at%20DAE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlants%20set%20up%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20River%20Ganga%20by%20Stellarin%20Venture%20Pvt.%20Ltd.%2C%20Raipur%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20can%20treat%20almost%201.5%20lakh%20liters%20of%20sewage%20a%20day%20at%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20site.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20Raipur%20based%20company%20has%20licensed%20this%20technology%20from%20India's%20nuclear%20establishment.%20Mr%20Arun%20Kumar%20Tiwari%2C%20Managing%20Director%20of%20the%20company%2C%20was%20earlier%20employed%20at%20BARC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20technology%20uses%20bacteria-laden%20granules%20(bio-beads)%20based%20treatment%20as%20a%20sustainable%20biological%20treatment%20alternative%20for%20waste%20water%20treatment%20plants%20(WWTP)%20over%20activated%20sludge%20systems%20due%20to%20high%20biomass%20retention%2C%20superior%20settling%20and%20treatment%20properties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20granules-based%20system%20can%20significantly%20cut-down%20the%20costs%20due%20to%20lower%20land%20footprint%2C%20lesser%20infrastructure%20and%20lower%20operational%20costs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20implementation%2C%20a%20novel%20method%20was%20developed%20for%20cultivating%20bio-beads%20-%20a%20combination%20of%20biofilms%20and%20granules%20--%20from%20wastewater-microbes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20superior%20treatment%2C%20it%20can%20lower%20the%20land%20footprint%20and%20costs%20by%20up%20to%2060%20per%20cent%20and%2030%20per%20cent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20benefits%20are%20huge%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20conventional%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20cuts%20down%20the%20volume%20of%20biological%20treatment%20tanks%20by%20up%20to%2020%20per%20cent%20as%20compared%20to%20conventional%20sequencing%20batch%20reactors%20(SBRs).%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnIt%20can%20help%20in%20accelerated%20bridging%20of%20the%20gap%20between%20sewage%20generation%20and%20treatment%20capacity%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20remarkable%20achievement%20since%20earlier%2C%20Kumbh's%20cholera%20and%20dysentery%20outbreaks%20were%20quite%20common%2C%20owing%20to%20open%20defecation%20and%20dirty%20water.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Government%20has%20made%201.5%20lakh%20toilets%20at%20the%20mela%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%2011%20permanent%20sewage%20treatment%20plants%20and%20three%20temporary%20ones%2C%20which%20are%20catering%20to%20the%20huge%20outflow%20of%20sewage%20at%20the%20mela%20site.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClean%20drinking%20water%20is%20being%20supplied%20through%20more%20than%20200%20water%20automatic%20dispensing%20machines.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739704380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fmpv1vvmo_jitendra-singh-kumbh_625x300_16_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fminister-on-how-nuclear-technology-is-helping-maintain-hygiene-at-kumbh-7723714%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22There%20is%20%26quot%3Bno%20sign%20of%20any%20disease%20outbreak%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20even%20though%20millions%20are%20taking%20a%20bath%20at%20Prayagraj%2C%20asserted%20the%20country's%20science%20minister%2C%20attributing%20it%20to%20the%20wonders%20of%20nuclear%20technology.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fminister-on-how-nuclear-technology-is-helping-maintain-hygiene-at-kumbh-7723714%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20troubling%20'self-fulfilling%20prophecy'%20may%20be%20forming%20a%20market%20bubble%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%20here's%20how%20investors%20can%20avoid%20the%20potentially%20dangerous%20domino%20effect%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224173%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Stock%20Market%20Bubble%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6013e7d16dfbe10018e00ab0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222582%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFears%20about%20a%20stock%20market%20bubble%20fueled%20by%20passive%20investing%20aren't%20going%20away%20anytime%20soon.%3Cp%3EJohannes%20Eisele%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPassive%20investing%20has%20been%20the%20dominant%20strategy%20for%20years%20as%20active%20funds%20lagged.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHowever%2C%20there's%20a%20major%20risk%20building%20as%20everyone%20plows%20money%20into%20index%20funds.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHere's%20why%20market%20observers%20see%20a%20bubble%20forming%20%E2%80%94%20and%20what%20could%20finally%20pop%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20investors%20who've%20done%20the%20least%20have%20performed%20the%20best.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20their%20best%20efforts%2C%20fund%20managers%20broadly%20have%20consistently%20trailed%20the%20market.%20Only%2030%25%20of%20actively%20managed%20global%20funds%20beat%20their%20indexes%20in%202024%2C%20according%20to%20Bank%20of%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS-based%20managers%20weren't%20much%20better.%20BofA%20found%20that%2036%25%20of%20active%20large-cap%20mutual%20funds%20in%20the%20US%20exceeded%20their%20benchmarks%20last%20year%2C%20in%20line%20with%20the%20long-term%20average%20of%2037%25.%20T