ght%2C%20in%20the%20short%20run%20imported%20consumer%20goods%20prices%20could%20go%20up%20-%20that%20shows%20up%20as%20inflation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20Indian%20manufacturers%20have%20to%20step%20up%20and%20set%20up%20capacity%20and%20%26quot%3Bacquire%20the%20know-how%20when%20needed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EAs%20a%20slightly%20oversimplified%20mental%20model%2C%20India%20exports%20software%20services%20to%20America%20and%20imports%20consumer%20goods%20from%20China.%20The%20surplus%20with%20America%20is%20more%20than%20matched%20by%20the%20deficit%20with%20China.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnNow%20India%20will%20(have%20to)%20import%20more%20iPhones%2C%20GPUs%2C%20LPG%2C%20nuclear%20plants%2C%20fighter%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Sridhar%20Vembu%20(%40svembu)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsvembu%2Fstatus%2F1890613306895085890%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2015%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia's%20Trade%20With%C2%A0US%20And%20China%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%2C%20India's%20trade%20surplus%20with%20the%20US%20has%20doubled%2C%20growing%20from%20%2417.30%20billion%20in%202019-20%20to%20%2435.33%20billion%20in%202023-24%2C%20alongside%20a%20notable%20shift%20in%20the%20export%20basket.%20While%20exports%20of%20electronic%20and%20engineering%20goods%20surged%2C%20traditional%20exports%20such%20as%20gems%2C%20jewellery%20and%20garments%20remained%20largely%20unchanged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20India's%20trade%20deficit%20with%20China%20has%20hit%20%2485.1%20billion%20in%20the%20fiscal%20year%202024%2C%20with%20imports%20from%20Beijing%20witnessing%20a%209.8%20per%20cent%20rise%20year-on-year%20between%20April%20and%20October%202024.%20China%20remains%20India's%20top%20import%20source%2C%20with%20imports%20valued%20at%20%2465.89%20billion%20during%20that%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20numbers%20underscore%20a%20growing%20economic%20concern%2C%20as%20exports%20to%20China%20fell%20to%20just%20%248%20billion%20during%20this%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump's%20Threats%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Trump%20on%20Saturday%20warned%20that%20%26quot%3BAmerica%20will%20charge%20a%20RECIPROCAL%20Tariff%2C%20meaning%2C%20whatever%20countries%20charge%20the%20United%20States%20of%20America%2C%20we%20will%20charge%20them-%20No%20more%2C%20no%20less!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Friday%2C%20highlighting%20the%20trade%20imbalance%20between%20Washington%20and%20New%20Delhi%2C%20the%20US%20President%20said%20that%20Indian%20tariffs%20as%20high%20as%2070%20per%20cent%20on%20American%20goods%20such%20as%20cars%20are%20a%20%26quot%3Bbig%20problem%26quot%3B.%20He%20pointed%20out%20that%20US%20sales%20of%20oil%20and%20gas%20will%20bridge%20the%20American%20trade%20deficit%20with%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20imposes%20a%2030%2C%2040%2C%2060%20and%20even%2070%20per%20cent%20tariff%20on%20so%20many%20goods%2C%20and%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20far%20more%20than%20that.%20As%20an%20example%2C%20a%2070%20per%20cent%20tariff%20on%20US%20cars%20going%20into%20India%20makes%20it%20pretty%20much%20impossible%20to%20sell%20those%20cars.%20Today%2C%20the%20US%20trade%20deficit%20with%20India%20is%20almost%20%24100%20billion%2C%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20and%20I%20have%20agreed%20that%20we%20will%20be%20negotiating%20to%20address%20the%20long-running%20disparities%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20a%20press%20briefing%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20a%20certain%20level%20playing%20field%2C%20which%20we%20really%20think%20we're%20entitled%20to%2C%20and%20he%20does%20also%2C%20in%20fairness.%20So%20we're%20going%20to%20work%20on%20that%20very%20hard%2C%20and%20we%20can%20make%20up%20the%20difference%20very%20easily%20with%20the%20deficit%2C%20with%20the%20sale%20of%20oil%20and%20gas%2C%20LNG%2C%20of%20which%20we%20have%20more%20than%20anybody%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Trump%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739702760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fldmgpcdg_sridhar-vembu_625x300_24_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Finflation-ahead-zoho-founder-sridhar-vembus-big-warning-as-trump-demands-reciprocal-trade-7723560%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20may%20witness%20some%20economic%20hardships%20amid%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20push%20for%20balancing%20bilateral%20trade%20with%20threats%20of%20reciprocal%20tariffs%2C%20warned%20Zoho%20founder%20Sridhar%20Vembu.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Finflation-ahead-zoho-founder-sridhar-vembus-big-warning-as-trump-demands-reciprocal-trade-7723560%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UAE%20Expands%20Visa-On-Arrival%20Facility%20For%20Indians%20From%206%20More%20Countries%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20(UAE)%20has%20expanded%20its%20visa-on-arrival%20programme%20for%20Indian%20nationals%20by%20including%20travellers%20with%20valid%20visas%2C%20residence%20permits%2C%20or%20Green%20Cards%20from%20six%20more%20countries%20on%20the%20eligibility%20list.%20The%20move%20permits%20more%20Indian%20passport%20holders%20to%20access%20visa-on-arrival%20facilities%20at%20UAE%20entry%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Arab%20country's%20latest%20order%2C%20Indians%20with%20valid%20visas%2C%20residence%20permits%2C%20or%20Green%20Cards%20from%20Singapore%2C%20Japan%2C%20South%20Korea%2C%20Australia%2C%20New%20Zealand%2C%20and%20Canada%20will%20be%20allowed%20access%20to%20the%20visa-on-arrival%20facility%