g-existing-homes-for-two-years%2Famp_articleshow%2F118301662.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWe%20Cannot%20Always...%26quot%3B%3A%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20On%20Why%20He%20Praised%20PM%20Modi-Trump%20Meet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress%20MP%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20on%20Saturday%20defended%20his%20praise%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20following%20his%20meeting%20with%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20stating%20that%20he%20spoke%20with%20India's%20interests%20in%20mind%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bwe%20cannot%20always%20speak%20only%20in%20terms%20of%20party%20interest.%26quot%3B%20Speaking%20to%20reporters%2C%20Mr%20Tharoor%20said%20that%20PM%20Modi's%20US%20visit%20had%20yielded%20some%20positive%20outcomes%20for%20the%20Indian%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20noted%20that%20PM%20Modi%20being%20the%20fourth%20world%20leader%20to%20meet%20Trump%20after%20he%20took%20office%20underscored%20India's%20growing%20importance%20on%20the%20global%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20visit%20left%20some%20questions%20unanswered%2C%20such%20as%20why%20the%20issue%20of%20how%20illegal%20immigrants%20were%20returned%20to%20India%20was%20not%20addressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDid%20PM%20Modi%20raise%20it%20behind%20closed%20doors%3F%20In%20diplomacy%2C%20not%20everything%20is%20laid%20out%20publicly%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Tharoor%2C%20the%20Congress%20MP%20from%20Thiruvananthapuram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWelcoming%20the%20agreement%20to%20hold%20trade%20and%20tariff%20negotiations%20over%20the%20next%20nine%20months%2C%20Mr%20Tharoor%20remarked%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20far%20better%20than%20Washington%20hastily%20and%20unilaterally%20imposing%20tariffs%20on%20us%2C%20which%20could%20have%20hurt%20our%20exports.%20To%20my%20mind%2C%20something%20good%20has%20been%20achieved%2C%20and%20I%20applaud%20that%20as%20an%20Indian.%20We%20can't%20always%20speak%20only%20in%20terms%20of%20party%20interests.%20I%20am%20not%20a%20party%20spokesman.%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Tharoor%20emphasised%20that%20as%20an%20elected%20MP%20representing%20Thiruvananthapuram%2C%20he%20speaks%20as%20a%20responsible%20stakeholder%20in%20Indian%20democracy%20and%20on%20behalf%20of%20those%20who%20have%20placed%20their%20trust%20in%20him%20to%20exercise%20his%20judgment%20and%20speak%20fairly%20and%20freely%20on%20certain%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20this%20particular%20case%2C%20I%20am%20speaking%20solely%20in%20the%20national%20interest%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tharoor%20further%20stated%20that%20throughout%20his%2016-year%20political%20career%2C%20his%20approach%20has%20remained%20consistent%3B%20acknowledging%20and%20praising%20good%20governance%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20party%20in%20power%2C%20while%20also%20criticising%20when%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20someone%20in%20government%2C%20whether%20from%20the%20Congress%20or%20any%20other%20party%2C%20does%20something%20right%2C%20it%20should%20be%20acknowledged%20and%20praised.%20When%20they%20do%20something%20wrong%2C%20it%20should%20be%20criticised%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20done%20both-I%20have%20praised%20and%20I%20have%20criticised.%20In%20fairness%2C%20I%20base%20my%20stance%20on%20facts.%20That%20I%20believe%20is%20the%20right%20approach.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%20that%20consistently%20praising%20or%20criticising%20the%20government%20would%20undermine%20his%20credibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20were%20to%20praise%20all%20the%20time%2C%20no%20one%20would%20take%20me%20seriously.%20If%20I%20were%20to%20criticise%20all%20the%20time%2C%20no%20one%20would%20take%20me%20seriously%20either%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tharoor%20also%20criticised%20the%20tendency%20of%20political%20parties%20to%20oppose%20each%20other%20reflexively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20real%20problem%20arises%20when%20the%20opposition%20believes%20everything%20the%20government%20does%20is%20wrong%2C%20and%20when%20the%20government%20believes%20everything%20the%20opposition%20says%20is%20wrong%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20has%20to%20be%20some%20give%20and%20take%20in%20a%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739702220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F2ph2j96g_shashi-tharoor_625x300_30_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findias-interest-shashi-tharoor-defends-his-praise-on-pm-modi-trump-meet-7722706%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20MP%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20on%20Saturday%20defended%20his%20praise%20for%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20following%20his%20meeting%20with%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findias-interest-shashi-tharoor-defends-his-praise-on-pm-modi-trump-meet-7722706%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kumbh-Bound%20Rush%20In%20UP%20Cities%2C%20Train%20Stations%20On%20Alert%20After%20Delhi%20Stampede%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh's%20Prayagraj%20and%20neighbouring%20cities%20continued%20to%20face%20massive%20traffic%20over%20the%20weekend%20as%20thousands%20of%20vehicles%20moved%20towards%20the%20city%20for%20the%20ongoing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fas-millions-head-to-maha-kumbh-an-extension-request-from-akhilesh-yadav-7716644%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMaha%20Kumbh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20has%20attracted%20more%20than%2050%20crore%20devotees%20since%20it%20began%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%