tate'%20Charges%2C%20US%20Cuts%20Bangladesh%20%26quot%3BPolitical%20Landscape%26quot%3B%20Funds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20bid%20to%20save%20US%20taxpayers'%20money%2C%20the%20Donald%20Trump%20administration's%20cost-cutting%20team--Department%20of%20Government%20Efficiency%20(DOGE)--%20has%20cancelled%20a%20slew%20of%20overseas%20projects%2C%20including%20one%20in%20Bangladesh%20that%20raised%20several%20eyebrows.%20The%20billionaire%20Elon%20Musk-led%20department%20said%20it%20is%20cancelling%20%2429%20million%20funding%20intended%20for%20%26quot%3Bstrengthening%20the%20political%20landscape%20in%20Bangladesh%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%20listing%20a%20list%20of%20cancelled%20US%20funding%20abroad%2C%20DOGE%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BUSD%2029M%20to%20'strengthening%20the%20political%20landscape%20in%20Bangladesh%26quot%3B%20has%20been%20stopped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EUS%20taxpayer%20dollars%20were%20going%20to%20be%20spent%20on%20the%20following%20items%2C%20all%20which%20have%20been%20cancelled%3A%3Cbr%3E%5Cn-%20%2410M%20for%20%26quot%3BMozambique%20voluntary%20medical%20male%20circumcision%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn-%20%249.7M%20for%20UC%20Berkeley%20to%20develop%20%26quot%3Ba%20cohort%20of%20Cambodian%20youth%20with%20enterprise%20driven%20skills%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn-%20%242.3M%20for%20%26quot%3Bstrengthening%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Department%20of%20Government%20Efficiency%20(%40DOGE)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDOGE%2Fstatus%2F1890849405932077378%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2015%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20days%20after%20American%20President%20Trump%20denied%20allegations%20of%20US%20involvement%20in%20the%20regime%20change%20in%20Bangladesh%20last%20year%20when%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20was%20ousted%20following%20a%20nationwide%20protest%20led%20by%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20Strengthening%20Political%20Landscape%20Project%20in%20Bangladesh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFunded%20by%20the%20United%20States%20Agency%20For%20International%20Development%20(USAID)%20and%20the%20United%20Kingdon's%20erstwhile%20Department%20for%20International%20Development%2C%20the%20strengthening%20Political%20Landscape%20in%20Bangladesh%20program%20(SPL)%20worked%20to%20build%20political%20party%20capacity%20and%20strengthen%20relationships%20between%20parties%20and%20constituents%20while%20reducing%20political%20violence%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22No%20Follow%2C%20No%20Index%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdemocracyinternational.com%2Fprojects%2Fbangladesh-strengthening-political-landscape%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDemocracy%20International%3C%2Fa%3E%20(DI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPer%20DI%2C%20the%20programme%20supported%20political%20activists%20and%20citizens%20as%20they%20built%20the%20skills%20they%20needed%20to%20become%20effective%20leaders%2C%20advocate%20for%20inclusive%20policies%2C%20and%20constructively%20engage%20with%20one%20another%20to%20mitigate%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20SPL%20confronted%20the%20challenges%20of%20political%20violence%20by%20engaging%20political%20parties%2C%20grassroots%20activists%2C%20and%20university%20students%2C%20monitoring%20incidents%20of%20violence%2C%20and%20promoting%20peaceful%20alternatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump%20On%20US%20Involvement%20In%20Bangadesh's%20Regime%20Change%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20bilateral%20meeting%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Thursday%2C%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20dismissed%20any%20American%20involvement%20in%20the%20Bangladesh%20political%20crisis%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20issue%20has%20been%20handled%20by%20India%20for%20a%20long%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20reporter%20sought%20the%20views%20of%20President%20Trump%20on%20whether%20the%20previous%20Democratic%20government%20under%20former%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20carried%20out%20a%20regime%20change%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20and%20installed%20Muhammad%20Yunus%20as%20a%20chief%20adviser%2C%20the%20Republican%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20role%20for%20our%20deep%20state.%20This%20is%20something%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20been%20working%20on%20for%20a%20long%20time%20and%20has%20worked%20on%20for%20hundreds%20of%20years...%20I%20have%20been%20reading%20about%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20pointing%20at%20PM%20Modi%20he%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20leave%20Bangladesh%20to%20the%20PM.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Republican%20did%20not%20directly%20address%20the%20question%2C%20speculation%20is%20that%20the%20response%20indicated%20the%20new%20Trump%20administration%20may%20not%20get%20itself%20involved%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20where%20alleged%20radical%20Islamist%20elements%20have%20been%20targeting%20religious%20minorities%20including%20Hindus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia-Bangladesh%20Relations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETies%20between%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%20have%20nosedived%20after%20Ms%20Hasina%20fled%20Dhaka%20in%20August%20in%20the%20face%20of%20a%20massive%20anti-government%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20interim%20government%20headed%20by%20Nobel%20laureate%20Muhammad%20Yunus%2C%20who%20returned%20from%20the%20US%20to%20work%20as%20Bangladesh's%20caretaker%2C%20continues%20to%20draw%20sharp%20criticism%20over%20not%20doing%20enough%20to%20stop%20attacks%20on%20minorities%20by%20radical%20Islamists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBangladesh-US%20Ties%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Bangladesh's%20Chief%20Adviser%2C%20Professor%20Muhammad%20Yunus%2C%20on%20Friday%20said%20that%20he%20has%20discussed%20with%20Tesla%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%20a%20potential%20collaboration%20to%20launch%20Starlink%20satellite%20internet%20service%20in%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYunus%20on%20Thursday%20held%20an%20extensive%20video%20discussion%20with%20Musk%20to%20make%20further%20progress%20in%20introducing%20Starlink%20satellite%20to%20enhance%20internet%20service%20in%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Yunus%20also%20extended%20an%20invitation%20to%20Musk%20to%20visit%20Bangladesh%20for%20the%20potential%20launch%20of%20Starlink%20services%2C%20underscoring%20the%20significance%20of%20this%20initiative%20for%20national%20development%2C%20to%20which%20Musk%20responded%20positively.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20look%20forward%20to%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20Biden-Era%20Funding%20Slashed%20By%20DOGE%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20the%20official%20DOGE%20handle%20listed%20the%20number%20of%20spending%20by%20US%20taxpayers%20that%20has%20been%20cancelled%2C%20including%20%2422%20million%20in%20funding%20intended%20for%20'voter%20turnout%20in%20India'%20and%20%24%2039%20million%20for%20%26quot%3Bfiscal%20federalism%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bbiodiversity%20conservation%26quot%3B%20in%20Nepal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20part%20of%20DOGE's%20continued%20effort%20to%20outline%20significant%20changes%20in%20government%20spending%20over%20the%20last%20few%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20Nepal's%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BFiscal%20Federalism%26quot%3B%20Programme%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20promulgation%20of%20the%202015%20constitution%2C%20Nepal%20embarked%20on%20its%20federalism%20journey%20and%20established%20three%20tiers%20of%20government--%20one%20federal%2C%20seven%20provinces%2C%20and%20753%20local%20levels%20in%202017.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fiscal%20federalism%20programme%20is%20based%20on%20the%20canon%20that%20%26quot%3Bsingle%20penny%20expense%20is%20not%20levied%20without%20the%20consent%20of%20parliament