dtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F112646-yashasvi-jaiswal-playerprofile%5C%22%3EYashasvi%20Jaiswal%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20chance%20at%20the%20top.%20But%2C%20an%20injury%20to%20Virat%20Kohli%20meant%20that%20Iyer%20played%20at%20the%20usual%20No.%203%20spot%2C%20cracking%20a%20fiery%20half-century.%20The%20batter%2C%20since%20then%2C%20became%20a%20regular%20for%20the%20remaining%20two%20matches%20of%20the%20series.%20But%2C%20there%20seems%20to%20be%20some%20conflict%20in%20the%20team%20management%20over%20Iyer's%20case%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20chat%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Findias-middle-order-a-concern-ahead-of-champions-trophy%2Farticleshow%2F118292491.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20former%20selector%20Devang%20Gandhi%20lauded%20India%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Gautam%20Gambhir%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F563-gautam-gambhir-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGautam%20Gambhir%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20helping%20the%20Indian%20team%20manage%20this%20transition%20but%20he%20also%20warned%20him%20to%20bring%20more%20consistency%20in%20the%20middle-order%20selection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGambhir%20must%20be%20given%20due%20credit%20for%20working%20with%20a%20team%20in%20transition.%20He%20has%20got%20India%20dominating%20in%20the%20ODI%20format%2C%20much%20like%20India%20were%20doing%20from%202016-2019.%20What%20the%20selectors%20and%20Gambhir%20need%20to%20be%20careful%20about%20is%20consistency%20in%20the%20middle%20order%2C%26quot%3B%20Gandhi%20told%20TOI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20batting%20then%20was%20largely%20driven%20by%20the%20top%20three%20-%20Rohit%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shikhar%20Dhawan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F737-shikhar-dhawan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShikhar%20Dhawan%3C%